name: ResultStatus
title: resultStatus
description: HL7-defined code system of concepts which specify a status of results for an order.  Used in HL7 Version 2.x messaging in the OBR segment.

concepts.display: Order received; specimen not yet received
No results available; specimen received, procedure incomplete
No results available; procedure scheduled, but not done
Some, but not all, results available

concepts.definition: A verified early result is available, final results not yet obtained
A result under an order, that has been finalized has been corrected
Final results; results stored and verified.

concepts.display: No order on record for this test
concepts.definition: No order on record for this test.
A result under an order, that has not yet been finalized has been corrected
No result available; requested procedure done.  To indicate that a requested test is performed but results are pending/not yet available.
